 <!-- Introduction -->
 <!-- The introduction should start as shown: -->
 <purpose>
   <p>
     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the
     representation of state-based behaviour models.  These contain entities for representing
     states, aggregations of states and state transitions.  Support is provided for the 
     representation of Moore and Mealy state machines as well as Statecharts.
   </p>
 </purpose>

